title: iPhone 15
description: iPhone 15 brings you Dynamic Island, a 48MP Main camera, and USB-C—all in a durable color-infused glass and aluminum design.
features: Dynamic island comes to iPhone 15—Experience a whole new way to interact with your iPhone. Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities, so you can see what's happening without leaving what you're doing.
Innovative design—iPhone 15 features a durable color-infused glass and aluminum design with a contoured edge. The Ceramic Shield front is tougher than any smartphone glass.
48MP Main camera with 2x telephoto—Capture super-high-resolution photos with the 48MP Main camera. And get closer to subjects with the 2x optical-quality Telephoto.
Next-generation portraits—Take portraits with more detail, better low-light performance, and rich, vibrant colors. Now you can shift the focus after you take the photo.
